==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncivil
<hw>Un*civ"il</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
civilized; savage; barbarous; uncivilized.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Men can not enjoy the rights of an <qex>uncivil</qex> and of a
civil state together.</q> <rj><qau>Burke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not civil; not complaisant; discourteous; impolite;
rude; unpolished; <as>as, <ex>uncivil</ex> behavior</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncivility</ent>⟦br⟧
